\SE[73]I'm glad you're safe... But I can't say this
situation is good. \SE[3]At best, if we can earn 5 minutes
with that level, it would be great.

Vega-sama... Laura-sama... May I ask for your assistance for
a moment?
(I wonder what she wants to convey.)

Ronoa, you know... She said, I'm glad to see you after such
a long time.

It seems like Lunaroa really likes this village... The
village chief is also kind.

I might understand Lunaroa's feelings a little. Maybe
because it's a little similar to Hatayaki Village.
